WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 19]

03:01.520 --> 03:02.140
Thank you.

03:08.910 --> 03:10.060
You're not some young couple anymore.

03:10.590 --> 03:11.770
Why are you thanking him?

03:13.710 --> 03:15.140
Let's get out of here first.

03:17.000 --> 03:17.690
Fine.

03:22.310 --> 03:23.420
I'll trust you for now.

03:25.400 --> 03:26.690
I agree to work with you.

03:27.800 --> 03:29.340
You can take the others.

03:30.630 --> 03:31.690
But not Lu Wuyi.

03:32.750 --> 03:33.370
Why?

03:34.630 --> 03:35.580
She matters to me

03:36.910 --> 03:37.900
more than anyone.

03:39.000 --> 03:40.900
Among the relics left in the Ruined Sand,

03:41.590 --> 03:43.300
there's a portrait of a mortal woman

03:43.310 --> 03:44.460
named Di Zhu.

03:45.630 --> 03:46.580
Lu Wuyi

03:47.240 --> 03:48.900
looks exactly like her.

03:49.910 --> 03:51.460
From the moment she was born in the Sacred Spring,

03:51.960 --> 03:53.340
you shaped her face

03:53.710 --> 03:55.180
like Di Zhu's.

03:56.080 --> 03:57.090
I never understood this before.

03:57.560 --> 03:58.530
You're Jiu Ying.

03:59.470 --> 04:01.490
You shouldn't be able to obtain

04:01.710 --> 04:03.460
their memories from the Primordial Sacred Spring.

04:04.030 --> 04:05.180
But now I see.

04:05.680 --> 04:07.060
You created Lu Wuyi

04:07.750 --> 04:08.360
to gather

04:08.360 --> 04:10.460
everyone's emotions and memories.

04:11.430 --> 04:13.420
Thus, you controlled the entire Formless Moon Sect.

04:13.910 --> 04:16.460
You made up the lie of a "fated one"

04:17.120 --> 04:18.300
and sent her to get close to me.

04:20.040 --> 04:20.570
What?

04:22.070 --> 04:22.810
Now that your plan works,

04:24.750 --> 04:26.660
you want to take her back from me?

04:27.190 --> 04:28.220
The plan works?

04:30.190 --> 04:31.930
You actually think Lu Wuyi likes you?

04:34.560 --> 04:35.370
Then

04:36.750 --> 04:39.100
why not let her stay with me

04:41.480 --> 04:42.180
and keep watching me?

04:51.680 --> 04:52.300
I'll take all of them

04:53.920 --> 04:55.100
with me.

04:59.390 --> 05:02.180
You're nothing more than leftover

05:02.680 --> 05:05.370
after I devoured your memories and spat you out.

05:06.310 --> 05:08.420
It was only my power

05:08.800 --> 05:11.330
that gave you this new body.

05:12.120 --> 05:14.370
You've always wanted to know who you are.

05:15.310 --> 05:17.330
But Bai Ze and Chi Wen,

05:18.270 --> 05:19.660
who knew the truth all along,

05:20.870 --> 05:22.100
kept it from you.

05:23.600 --> 05:25.100
Your Master Dragon Deity

05:26.120 --> 05:27.860
knew your confusion

05:28.480 --> 05:29.620
and your doubts.

05:30.870 --> 05:32.690
And yet he said nothing.

05:33.630 --> 05:36.130
He simply let you go on playing the commander,

05:36.920 --> 05:38.370
serving him,

05:38.720 --> 05:40.130
fighting for him,

05:40.310 --> 05:41.330
and dying for him.

05:43.720 --> 05:44.690
Just like

05:47.390 --> 05:48.860
he did with Ji Ling.

05:52.920 --> 05:54.010
How pitiful.

05:59.120 --> 06:01.450
I have one more secret to tell you.

06:03.160 --> 06:04.100
Come closer.

06:24.630 --> 06:26.130
This body

06:28.160 --> 06:29.780
won't last much longer.

06:33.430 --> 06:35.300
Heavenly Sticks can see fate

06:35.630 --> 06:36.420
and destiny.

06:36.800 --> 06:39.180
Prying into fate comes at a cost.

06:39.600 --> 06:40.420
Every divination

06:40.830 --> 06:42.100
must be paid for with one's own power

06:42.390 --> 06:43.250
and lifespan.

06:45.600 --> 06:47.060
Since you're here,

06:52.510 --> 06:54.330
shall we exchange bodies?

09:04.200 --> 09:04.810
Wangyan,

09:05.720 --> 09:06.930
what do we do next?

09:10.870 --> 09:12.180
Destroy the Oracle Stone.

09:13.490 --> 09:15.610
Kill Jiu Ying, who's attached to it.

09:19.960 --> 09:21.570
But when the next full moon comes,

09:22.120 --> 09:23.850
we'll still be summoned back to the Formless Moon Sect.

09:26.510 --> 09:27.780
If we fail

09:28.750 --> 09:29.900
before then...

09:31.630 --> 09:32.810
We'll have to

09:35.240 --> 09:35.970
sever our tails.

09:48.960 --> 09:49.690
Looks like

09:50.790 --> 09:52.300
he knows who he is now.

09:54.200 --> 09:55.900
I know who I am too.

10:11.500 --> 10:18.020
♪So many dawns and dusks in pouring rain♪

10:18.380 --> 10:20.980
♪Twilight weighs down beyond our sight♪

10:20.980 --> 10:24.860
♪Trapping us small souls so tight...♪

10:27.150 --> 10:28.500
Body returns to dust.

10:29.510 --> 10:30.900
Spirit is carried away by the wind.

10:33.150 --> 10:35.020
May you be freed from your obsessions,

10:36.030 --> 10:36.810
and in your next life,

10:38.000 --> 10:39.140
live long, healthy,

10:41.750 --> 10:42.730
and in peace.

10:48.440 --> 10:49.210
You left your blade

10:50.030 --> 10:51.450
in Ruined Sand,

10:51.870 --> 10:52.730
didn't you?

11:04.720 --> 11:06.020
I'll go with you.

11:35.510 --> 11:36.540
I should've brought it back

11:36.540 --> 11:38.690
to the Shilin Sect for you.

11:40.080 --> 11:41.500
But no one but you

11:42.240 --> 11:43.930
can wield the Mountain Demon Blade.

11:48.750 --> 11:49.450
Go retrieve it.

11:54.840 --> 11:55.660
Is there a problem?

12:13.480 --> 12:14.500
That six-eyed butterfly demon

12:14.670 --> 12:16.690
called himself Yuan Wuhuo.

12:17.320 --> 12:19.380
He looks exactly

12:19.480 --> 12:20.380
like Commander Li.

12:34.030 --> 12:34.660
What is it?

12:40.870 --> 12:41.570
Nothing.

12:42.870 --> 12:44.300
It reminded me of back then,

12:44.360 --> 12:45.930
when you sent me to Mount Nandang

12:46.550 --> 12:47.660
to pull out the blade.

12:48.390 --> 12:49.540
That's how I got this weapon,

12:49.910 --> 12:51.900
which has stayed by my side ever since.

12:59.980 --> 13:01.460
♪Black and white, they say♪

13:01.780 --> 13:04.460
♪Look, the sky shimmers in color♪

13:04.980 --> 13:06.420
♪So many stars♪

13:06.860 --> 13:10.060
♪Each one was once me♪

13:10.300 --> 13:12.460
♪Watching the sunset♪

13:12.820 --> 13:14.940
♪Burning stubbornly♪

13:15.300 --> 13:19.420
♪A trace of crimson remembers me♪

13:20.260 --> 13:24.980
♪I wish someone would remember me♪

13:25.300 --> 13:30.780
♪I just need you to remember me♪

13:46.960 --> 13:48.060
I've checked it.

13:48.910 --> 13:50.180
He's not Yuan Wuhuo.

13:52.120 --> 13:52.810
That's good.

13:54.080 --> 13:54.780
What about you?

13:55.960 --> 13:56.730
Are you alright?

14:00.750 --> 14:01.570
You know full well

14:03.030 --> 14:03.840
the Dragon Deity's Power

14:03.840 --> 14:05.300
has long blended

14:05.300 --> 14:06.090
with your own demon power.

14:07.510 --> 14:08.500
If you try to separate it,

14:09.840 --> 14:10.810
the backlash will be fatal.

14:11.910 --> 14:12.850
You can't be saved.

14:15.630 --> 14:16.900
I've given all my demon power

14:16.900 --> 14:17.930
to protect my inner core.

14:19.480 --> 14:20.180
I can still

14:20.870 --> 14:22.500
hold on a little longer.

14:38.870 --> 14:39.540
I want

14:40.480 --> 14:42.020
to walk this final journey with you.

14:44.910 --> 14:45.930
Don't worry about me.

14:47.510 --> 14:48.730
Wu Shiguang is waiting for you.

14:55.910 --> 14:56.780
Go to Luo'an.

14:57.840 --> 14:59.020
Take back the last trace of Dragon Deity's Power

14:59.020 --> 15:00.450
from Han Ba.

15:38.910 --> 15:39.540
Wangyan,

15:41.000 --> 15:41.930
what kind of secret

15:42.670 --> 15:44.260
do the two dragons share?

15:44.870 --> 15:46.210
Why did they hide it from us?

15:48.670 --> 15:50.420
Probably

15:50.510 --> 15:52.330
just something between men.

15:54.720 --> 15:55.660
Don't overthink it.

15:56.120 --> 15:57.380
We've kept plenty

15:57.390 --> 15:59.180
from them too.

16:11.550 --> 16:13.300
You came all this way

16:13.440 --> 16:14.850
because you heard I was captured by Jiu Ying?

16:16.510 --> 16:17.660
I was worried

16:17.870 --> 16:19.450
you'd get skinned and turned into a fox-fur coat.

16:20.000 --> 16:21.300
Too bad I was late.

16:21.750 --> 16:23.660
Missed my chance to play the hero.

16:25.080 --> 16:26.330
Hero,

16:27.000 --> 16:27.970
what's your name?

16:29.360 --> 16:30.300
Call me sister.

16:32.840 --> 16:33.970
I only have one sister.

16:35.360 --> 16:36.690
Greedy Wolf Demon Hunter of the Northern Dipper.

16:37.000 --> 16:37.570
Si Feng.

16:39.510 --> 16:40.500
I can tell.

16:41.550 --> 16:43.380
That double-flower mark on her forehead is hard to miss.

16:44.550 --> 16:46.180
Since when did a thousand-year-old fox like you

16:46.670 --> 16:47.730
get so close

16:47.910 --> 16:49.160
to a ruthless demon hunter

16:49.160 --> 16:50.980
from the Big Dipper?

16:51.840 --> 16:52.900
I didn't know that.

16:57.200 --> 16:58.570
Honestly, neither did I.

17:01.840 --> 17:03.020
What has happened?

17:18.960 --> 17:20.260
Were you waiting for me?

17:20.960 --> 17:21.540
I was.

17:25.590 --> 17:26.850
And you are?

17:28.350 --> 17:29.220
What's the matter?

17:30.750 --> 17:31.610
You're at it again.

17:32.110 --> 17:33.260
We've met before.

17:33.680 --> 17:34.500
Many times.

17:36.200 --> 17:37.410
If I'd met someone as powerful as you

17:37.590 --> 17:38.940
that often,

17:39.350 --> 17:40.540
I wouldn't have forgotten.

17:40.680 --> 17:42.220
What if your memory was erased?

17:43.790 --> 17:45.500
Master Chi Wen left you a message.

17:46.440 --> 17:47.980
The Oracle Stone can't be trusted.

17:49.030 --> 17:50.130
If you have doubts,

17:50.350 --> 17:51.310
seal away part of your memory

17:51.310 --> 17:52.850
inside this artifact.

17:53.070 --> 17:54.130
Retrieve it later,

17:54.960 --> 17:56.020
and it'll remind you of the truth.

18:06.640 --> 18:07.610
Let me remind you of something.

18:08.240 --> 18:09.370
The first time we met

18:09.960 --> 18:11.130
was because of Han Ba.

18:13.200 --> 18:14.090
Han Ba?

18:19.000 --> 18:20.610
Have you figured out

18:21.030 --> 18:22.540
why Jiu Ying erased the memory

18:22.540 --> 18:24.700
of our first meeting?

18:26.310 --> 18:26.850
No.

18:28.750 --> 18:29.940
I only know

18:30.350 --> 18:31.780
I was on a mission.

18:32.510 --> 18:33.260
A mission?

18:35.440 --> 18:37.610
We always act together.

18:37.790 --> 18:39.020
We've never taken solo missions.

18:39.480 --> 18:40.810
That's strange.

18:41.480 --> 18:42.170
But

18:42.750 --> 18:45.370
we're heading to Luo'an soon to find Han Ba.

18:46.160 --> 18:46.980
When we get there,

18:47.640 --> 18:49.220
we'll get to the bottom of this.

18:51.510 --> 18:52.570
I've seen

18:53.830 --> 18:54.740
all of Chi Wen's memories.

18:57.000 --> 18:58.370
What did you see?

19:00.400 --> 19:01.700
No one here should sacrifice yourselves.

19:02.400 --> 19:03.570
There's another way.

19:04.510 --> 19:07.010
Just lend me your demon power.

19:07.750 --> 19:08.980
As for returning the deity power,

19:09.640 --> 19:10.500
I have

19:11.030 --> 19:12.060
my own plan.

19:14.070 --> 19:15.020
You're free.

19:16.440 --> 19:17.980
Your will is your own.

19:18.920 --> 19:21.330
Whether you choose slaughter or protection,

19:22.480 --> 19:23.810
that's up to you.

19:25.160 --> 19:27.610
Fuse our reverse scales together

19:28.440 --> 19:30.170
and create the Tenth Dragon Son.

19:31.790 --> 19:35.170
That will be our final hope for this world.

19:35.720 --> 19:36.940
You're not Chi Wen.

19:39.790 --> 19:40.940
And you're not my brother.

19:43.790 --> 19:46.330
From now on, you're neither demon

19:46.640 --> 19:47.610
nor human.

19:48.590 --> 19:50.410
You are Chi Wen.

19:51.200 --> 19:53.090
The last Dragon Deity in this world.

19:54.830 --> 19:56.460
But you've been carrying

19:56.750 --> 19:58.540
the burden my brothers left you,

20:00.000 --> 20:01.610
the hopes of the world,

20:03.640 --> 20:05.330
and a lie meant to deceive it.

20:07.070 --> 20:08.370
I know you've been waiting for me.

20:09.590 --> 20:12.540
How long must I keep lying?

20:14.030 --> 20:15.650
Until the Tenth Dragon Son awakens

20:15.750 --> 20:17.170
and becomes a true dragon.

20:17.830 --> 20:20.220
Only then will your mission end.

20:21.960 --> 20:23.610
The Tenth Dragon Son?

20:31.830 --> 20:32.540
I'm sorry.

20:36.720 --> 20:38.170
I made you wait so long.

20:44.720 --> 20:46.890
It has been a long time.

20:51.880 --> 20:52.810
Too long.

21:02.920 --> 21:03.810
But at least

21:07.070 --> 21:08.060
you're here now.

21:09.640 --> 21:11.260
Once the Dragon Deity's Power is complete

21:11.680 --> 21:13.170
and you return to your rightful place,

21:15.270 --> 21:17.060
I can finally lay this burden down.

21:20.880 --> 21:22.810
Everyone calls you Master Chi Wen.

21:24.590 --> 21:25.780
But what is your real name?

21:27.680 --> 21:29.260
Before you became Master Dragon Deity,

21:30.680 --> 21:31.300
who were you?

21:40.720 --> 21:41.330
Ji Ling.

21:46.480 --> 21:47.610
My name is

21:52.200 --> 21:52.890
Ji Ling.

21:56.310 --> 21:57.780
Ji, as in "a fleeting life".

21:58.920 --> 22:00.220
Ling, as in "a kindred understanding".

22:00.580 --> 22:06.220
♪Clad in golden scales, I gaze from the valley high...♪

22:07.680 --> 22:08.260
Sir,

22:09.280 --> 22:09.980
what's your name?

22:10.590 --> 22:11.260
My name is Ji Ling.

22:11.510 --> 22:12.410
Ji, as in "a fleeting life".

22:12.510 --> 22:13.260
Ling, as in "a kindred understanding".

22:13.260 --> 22:14.660
♪Through all joys and sorrows♪

22:14.820 --> 22:16.380
♪Bitter and sweet♪

22:16.580 --> 22:19.740
♪The moon stays by my side♪

22:20.180 --> 22:25.980
♪Its light is my most precious scale♪

22:33.060 --> 22:38.500
♪The moon accompanies me as I roam the mortal world…♪

22:38.510 --> 22:39.260
I knew it.

22:41.240 --> 22:42.300
You are Ji Ling.

22:44.400 --> 22:45.060
Ji Ling.

22:47.000 --> 22:47.940
One day,

22:50.510 --> 22:51.780
you'll admit it yourself.

22:52.830 --> 22:54.650
I'll ask you one last time.

22:56.070 --> 22:56.540
Are you

22:57.830 --> 22:59.130
Ji Ling?

22:59.720 --> 23:01.090
Give Ji Ling back to me.

23:01.960 --> 23:02.780
Give him back!

23:03.830 --> 23:04.780
Are you

23:06.110 --> 23:07.980
Ji Ling?

23:09.240 --> 23:09.850
No.

23:10.510 --> 23:11.500
I'm not Ji Ling.

23:12.240 --> 23:13.060
I'm not Ji Ling.

23:14.550 --> 23:15.740
You are Ji Ling.

23:18.960 --> 23:19.500
You are

23:20.660 --> 23:23.580
♪As time drifts farther away…♪

23:24.680 --> 23:25.700
Ji Ling.

23:30.060 --> 23:33.180
♪At the ends of the world, distant peaks, or endless roads♪

23:33.380 --> 23:36.780
♪The moon is always by my side♪

23:37.020 --> 23:44.060
♪I want wildflowers to bloom far and wide♪

24:24.240 --> 24:25.410
Why did you make

24:25.480 --> 24:26.740
all these puppets?

24:32.720 --> 24:34.130
Since I became the Dragon Deity,

24:35.000 --> 24:36.460
I've rarely left the Scale Cave.

24:37.440 --> 24:38.980
The Dragon Deity may be immortal

24:40.070 --> 24:42.540
and free to roam the world,

24:43.590 --> 24:44.700
but I

24:46.680 --> 24:48.260
was just an ordinary fox.

24:49.440 --> 24:50.650
You're a fox too?

24:54.480 --> 24:55.130
But

24:57.270 --> 24:59.650
not a noble nine-tailed fox from Green Hills like you.

25:00.310 --> 25:01.630
I was just

25:01.720 --> 25:04.060
a foolish red fox

25:04.830 --> 25:06.220
born by Yumian Lake.

25:14.790 --> 25:15.940
A wild fox?

25:16.830 --> 25:17.810
That's cute.

25:24.440 --> 25:26.500
If I were killed out there by demons,

25:27.160 --> 25:28.170
my disguise as the Dragon Deity

25:28.750 --> 25:29.940
would fall apart.

25:31.440 --> 25:33.090
I've stayed in this cave so long.

25:34.830 --> 25:36.780
I keep thinking about who I used to be.

25:38.310 --> 25:39.410
Back then,

25:40.000 --> 25:40.570
I was naïve

25:41.270 --> 25:41.850
and childish.

25:44.000 --> 25:44.780
But I lived every moment

25:44.920 --> 25:46.260
sincerely.

25:47.400 --> 25:48.460
I was simpler

25:48.960 --> 25:49.850
and freer than I am now.

25:50.750 --> 25:51.540
Like

25:52.720 --> 25:54.610
the warm summer wind brushes through the trees.

25:57.960 --> 25:58.890
Back then,

26:00.240 --> 26:01.220
I knew little,

26:02.640 --> 26:03.570
so I had fewer regrets.

26:04.830 --> 26:06.020
The worst thing

26:06.550 --> 26:07.540
was just

26:07.720 --> 26:08.850
not getting fresh raspberries

26:08.850 --> 26:10.260
in winter.

26:12.960 --> 26:13.570
Later,

26:14.680 --> 26:16.460
I came across an old spell

26:17.240 --> 26:18.850
in the ancient scrolls of Wanlin Pavilion.

26:20.510 --> 26:21.500
It has a beautiful name.

26:23.030 --> 26:23.980
Severed Silk.

26:27.510 --> 26:29.650
It takes a piece of one's life

26:31.110 --> 26:32.330
and cuts it out,

26:33.830 --> 26:35.780
like trimming fabric

26:36.030 --> 26:37.130
and weaving patterns into silk.

26:38.350 --> 26:39.260
Once separated,

26:39.480 --> 26:41.460
that piece becomes its own being,

26:41.880 --> 26:44.220
bearing the same appearance,

26:44.510 --> 26:45.220
personality,

26:45.510 --> 26:46.300
and memories as its owner,

26:48.510 --> 26:50.060
only without life.

27:20.700 --> 27:22.260
♪One winter day♪

27:22.660 --> 27:26.820
♪By the lake, a boy in white opened his eyes♪

27:27.100 --> 27:33.020
♪He gazed at the sky, watching fate spin by...♪

27:33.030 --> 27:33.740
So

27:34.270 --> 27:36.090
the Ji Ling you met was created that way.

27:37.110 --> 27:38.370
Are you a demon hunter from the mortal world?

27:39.440 --> 27:40.700
I'm a demon hunter of the Shilin Sect.

27:41.750 --> 27:42.780
I sent him out

27:42.960 --> 27:44.810
to feel the mountain winds,

27:45.400 --> 27:46.370
the life of the mortal world,

27:50.070 --> 27:51.060
joy,

27:52.680 --> 27:53.610
sorrow,

27:55.240 --> 27:56.260
adventure,

27:58.350 --> 27:59.170
and love.

27:59.340 --> 28:00.740
♪Through all joys and sorrows♪

28:00.900 --> 28:02.460
♪Bitter and sweet...♪

28:04.070 --> 28:05.220
He lived that life in my place

28:06.000 --> 28:07.810
to experience

28:09.070 --> 28:10.300
a colorful life.

28:19.180 --> 28:26.700
♪She looks at me and says, you're not alone tonight♪

28:36.960 --> 28:38.980
He'd go out, then return,

28:40.070 --> 28:42.330
bringing the lively world outside to me,

28:43.920 --> 28:45.540
while I stay in solitude.

28:51.200 --> 28:53.130
Then how did you end up in the Shilin Sect?

28:54.400 --> 28:55.940
How did you become the Dragon Deity?

28:58.270 --> 29:00.300
When the meteor blast happened,

29:01.070 --> 29:02.060
the earth shook.

29:03.200 --> 29:04.330
I was blind since childhood.

29:05.830 --> 29:07.780
I couldn't see the rocks falling

29:08.270 --> 29:09.220
and failed to escape.

29:10.030 --> 29:12.260
I was buried under rubble at the foot of South Mountain.

29:22.200 --> 29:23.610
Master Chi Wen saved me.

29:24.550 --> 29:25.810
He took pity on me

29:26.830 --> 29:28.780
and said a blind little fox like me

29:29.200 --> 29:30.300
couldn't survive

29:32.310 --> 29:33.090
on my own.

29:34.680 --> 29:36.060
So he brought me

29:36.240 --> 29:37.500
to the disaster site

29:38.790 --> 29:40.610
and granted me a healing spell

29:42.550 --> 29:44.130
so that I could help others.

29:56.160 --> 29:57.020
Sadly,

29:58.720 --> 30:01.090
I was too young and couldn't take human form.

30:03.160 --> 30:05.260
The power he gave me was limited.

30:06.070 --> 30:06.740
Once it was used up,

30:07.790 --> 30:08.410
that was it.

30:09.350 --> 30:10.260
So

30:12.000 --> 30:12.850
some people

30:15.070 --> 30:16.850
couldn't be saved.

30:18.550 --> 30:19.060
Xizai.

30:20.070 --> 30:20.650
Xizai.

30:22.000 --> 30:22.570
Xizai!

30:24.070 --> 30:24.610
Xizai!

30:26.000 --> 30:26.570
Xizai!

30:30.200 --> 30:30.890
Where's your sacred power?

30:31.590 --> 30:32.330
Save him!

30:32.920 --> 30:33.540
Come on!

30:47.750 --> 30:48.610
Save my brother.

30:49.550 --> 30:50.460
And I'll let you go.

31:22.550 --> 31:23.500
What happened after that?

31:36.790 --> 31:37.650
Wangyan and the others

31:37.750 --> 31:39.060
are waiting for us.

31:40.510 --> 31:41.650
That story

31:42.680 --> 31:43.740
is too long.

31:44.680 --> 31:46.060
I could talk day and night and still not finish it.

31:46.720 --> 31:47.780
Once we return from Luo'an,

31:48.790 --> 31:49.940
I'll tell you slowly.

31:52.590 --> 31:53.300
Promise.

32:03.070 --> 32:05.740
That's childish, wild fox.

32:12.110 --> 32:12.890
In the past,

32:13.480 --> 32:14.980
only Li Jie and the Four Great Demons

32:15.000 --> 32:16.410
knew I wasn't the Dragon Deity.

32:17.270 --> 32:18.260
Now that it's out in the open,

32:19.070 --> 32:20.300
I actually feel a lot lighter.

32:21.440 --> 32:22.370
From now on,

32:24.110 --> 32:25.330
I'll call you Ji Ling.

32:25.960 --> 32:26.540
Is that alright?

32:34.160 --> 32:35.170
Can you

32:36.480 --> 32:37.500
give me this doll?

32:41.070 --> 32:42.810
I can trade you something else for it.

32:47.790 --> 32:48.780
This little fox

32:50.350 --> 32:51.810
is the most precious thing I own.

32:52.550 --> 32:54.220
Nothing is worth trading for it.

32:55.310 --> 32:55.980
Back then,

32:56.790 --> 32:58.260
when I was imprisoned here,

32:58.720 --> 33:00.130
it was the one that stayed with me

33:00.880 --> 33:02.540
through those dark days.

33:04.110 --> 33:05.220
I even thought...

33:14.590 --> 33:15.540
What was it?

33:19.550 --> 33:20.460
It saved me.

33:24.720 --> 33:26.570
When I was at my lowest,

33:26.720 --> 33:27.460
it comforted me

33:28.110 --> 33:29.260
and gave me the courage

33:29.960 --> 33:31.060
to go on.

33:34.510 --> 33:36.170
How could a rag doll comfort you?

33:36.720 --> 33:38.170
Don't tell me it talks.

33:38.790 --> 33:39.780
It really does.

33:41.640 --> 33:42.130
See?

33:42.720 --> 33:44.500
I knew you'd react like that.

33:45.270 --> 33:46.650
No one ever believes me.

33:46.880 --> 33:47.780
But it's true.

33:54.880 --> 33:55.810
Whenever my tears

33:56.720 --> 33:58.260
fell on it,

33:59.680 --> 34:00.880
it was like it could feel

34:00.880 --> 34:01.940
my sadness.

34:05.400 --> 34:07.330
It would make soft sounds like a real fox.

34:08.480 --> 34:10.020
Awu... awu...

34:11.310 --> 34:12.460
It was telling me,

34:13.960 --> 34:14.820
"Don't cry.

34:16.760 --> 34:17.730
Don't be sad.

34:19.760 --> 34:21.210
I'll stay with you."

34:25.760 --> 34:26.650
That's ridiculous.

34:27.630 --> 34:28.650
If it were real,

34:29.190 --> 34:30.500
someone must've cast a spell on it.

34:42.360 --> 34:43.350
You're messing with me again, aren't you?

34:47.320 --> 34:48.380
I'm not lying.

34:49.880 --> 34:53.290
Maybe it's because you're here.

34:54.000 --> 34:55.090
It's shy.

34:57.380 --> 34:58.340
But

34:58.800 --> 35:00.060
I haven't heard its voice

35:00.060 --> 35:00.940
in a long time.

35:11.400 --> 35:11.860
Here.

35:20.920 --> 35:22.570
Isn't this your most treasured thing?

35:23.550 --> 35:24.380
You said you wouldn't trade it.

35:25.480 --> 35:25.900
That's right.

35:27.030 --> 35:27.650
I wouldn't trade it.

35:31.400 --> 35:33.130
I'm not asking for anything

35:33.510 --> 35:34.290
in return.

35:35.760 --> 35:37.340
I'm giving it to you because I want to.

35:38.590 --> 35:39.210
Right now,

35:39.800 --> 35:40.940
there's nothing more precious to me

35:41.000 --> 35:41.980
than you.

35:45.030 --> 35:46.090
Whatever you want,

35:47.630 --> 35:49.210
I'll get it for you.

35:51.630 --> 35:52.940
I want your heart.

35:53.670 --> 35:54.500
Will you give me that too?

35:56.320 --> 35:56.770
Yes.

36:01.360 --> 36:02.290
Master Dragon Deity,

36:03.440 --> 36:04.380
what's gotten into you?

36:05.400 --> 36:06.570
You weren't like this before.

36:07.150 --> 36:08.340
You've got quite a smooth tongue.

36:09.590 --> 36:10.730
I'll say

36:11.920 --> 36:12.980
whatever you want to hear.

36:13.880 --> 36:15.090
I'll do anything

36:15.840 --> 36:16.690
for you.

36:19.710 --> 36:21.340
I want the stars

36:22.360 --> 36:23.060
and the moon.

36:28.400 --> 36:29.340
I'll find a way.

36:32.630 --> 36:33.540
Master Dragon Deity,

36:35.960 --> 36:37.500
something's wrong with you.

36:40.360 --> 36:41.940
You've become a different person.

36:43.400 --> 36:44.170
I haven't changed.

36:46.070 --> 36:47.060
I'm Ji Ling.

36:56.190 --> 36:56.900
Before

36:58.670 --> 36:59.340
or now,

37:01.280 --> 37:02.940
all I ever wanted was for you to be happy.

37:59.150 --> 38:00.090
Get some rest.

38:00.960 --> 38:02.860
We leave for Luo'an tomorrow morning.

38:05.320 --> 38:06.540
You gave me the little fox,

38:07.510 --> 38:08.980
so I'll give you something in return.

38:10.630 --> 38:11.290
But first,

38:12.480 --> 38:13.900
close your eyes.

38:36.320 --> 38:37.000
Alright.

38:42.800 --> 38:43.820
What are you thinking about?

38:46.320 --> 38:46.860
I...

38:59.000 --> 38:59.820
I've put it on.

39:01.150 --> 39:02.500
You're not allowed to run away in this lifetime.

39:03.020 --> 39:08.700
♪From now on, you'll never grow old♪

39:09.060 --> 39:14.260
♪Even with earth between us, I'll softly sing with you♪

39:16.340 --> 39:19.460
♪In spring, I'll gather a thousand flowers for you♪

39:19.780 --> 39:22.460
♪In winter, I'll boil snow to warm the fading dusk...♪

39:22.880 --> 39:23.730
What is this?

39:25.760 --> 39:27.020
This is also something I treasure.

39:29.800 --> 39:31.170
They're Twin Luminous Cicadas.

39:32.550 --> 39:33.930
They come as a pair.

39:34.800 --> 39:36.150
No matter how far apart they are,

39:37.070 --> 39:38.570
if one lights up,

39:39.440 --> 39:40.380
the other will glow as well.

39:43.420 --> 39:46.500
♪The white-haired one looks on through tear-blurred eyes♪

39:46.860 --> 39:49.700
♪Sighing for youth, when words defied the heart...♪

39:49.710 --> 39:51.060
If you miss me,

39:51.670 --> 39:52.540
tap it.

39:54.480 --> 39:55.940
As long as I see it light up,

39:57.230 --> 39:58.130
I'll know

40:00.150 --> 40:01.020
you're thinking of me.

40:02.020 --> 40:06.500
♪Heavy snow falls, silver light shimmering through the world♪

40:08.060 --> 40:13.340
♪On the lake of the heart drifts a withered lotus leaf♪

40:14.620 --> 40:17.780
♪A young man sits alone with his back turned...♪

40:18.670 --> 40:19.720
Why has your scent

40:19.720 --> 40:20.650
grown fainter?

40:23.630 --> 40:24.380
You're being silly again.

40:28.260 --> 40:31.180
♪My vow burns forever♪

40:31.620 --> 40:34.500
♪Moths live to burn♪

40:35.020 --> 40:41.300
♪Unafraid to lose you again and again through every life♪

41:14.190 --> 41:15.060
I didn't expect

41:16.110 --> 41:17.170
the Master Bai Ze

41:17.440 --> 41:19.060
who knows all things in the world

41:20.070 --> 41:21.210
would still need to read books.

41:25.150 --> 41:26.260
I'm looking for an ancient way

41:26.260 --> 41:27.690
to extend one's lifespan.

41:29.150 --> 41:30.460
Master Dragon Deity, if I can't walk with you

41:31.360 --> 41:33.340
to the very end of your life,

41:35.360 --> 41:36.540
that would be my regret.

41:41.920 --> 41:43.090
You're still calling me that?

41:45.800 --> 41:46.770
In my heart,

41:48.190 --> 41:49.540
you are Master Dragon Deity.

41:56.190 --> 41:57.020
So,

41:58.880 --> 42:00.150
old man,

42:01.230 --> 42:02.460
you'd better stay alive.

42:08.400 --> 42:10.420
The last three spirit fragments of Jiu Ying

42:10.590 --> 42:11.420
have been found.

42:12.880 --> 42:13.570
One

42:15.670 --> 42:16.940
is inside Wu Shiguang.

42:18.550 --> 42:19.210
One

42:19.510 --> 42:20.460
is inside the Oracle Stone.

42:24.190 --> 42:25.420
Only one remains,

42:28.880 --> 42:30.020
I've checked it.

42:32.920 --> 42:34.250
It's inside Lu Wuyi.

42:39.960 --> 42:41.210
Inside the Star Stone illusion,

42:42.670 --> 42:43.570
none of us

42:44.480 --> 42:46.170
could use our powers.

42:47.150 --> 42:48.020
But Lu Wuyi

42:48.280 --> 42:49.980
could still use Word Magic

42:50.670 --> 42:51.570
and Frost Spell.

42:52.590 --> 42:53.210
And yet

42:54.110 --> 42:55.900
her power came and went.

42:57.030 --> 42:58.170
It was unstable.

42:59.510 --> 43:00.210
It didn't take long

43:01.000 --> 43:02.250
for me to understand why.

43:02.880 --> 43:04.420
Only when that little snake,

43:05.110 --> 43:06.860
Little Nine, was nearby...

43:07.280 --> 43:08.500
That's intense.

43:08.710 --> 43:09.690
Could she cast her spells.

43:19.000 --> 43:20.170
And when Little Nine moved away,

43:22.320 --> 43:23.690
her power vanished.

43:24.320 --> 43:25.090
What happened to my power?

43:31.480 --> 43:32.650
That little snake

43:33.840 --> 43:34.980
is Jiu Ying.

43:36.280 --> 43:37.460
So you suspect

43:38.190 --> 43:39.540
Lu Wuyi and Jiu Ying

43:40.000 --> 43:41.770
share some unique bond,

43:42.510 --> 43:44.090
which is why she can use power?

43:44.760 --> 43:45.250
Exactly.

43:46.400 --> 43:47.540
I questioned Jiu Ying

43:47.760 --> 43:48.690
in the Formless Moon Palace.

43:50.110 --> 43:51.290
Now I understand.

43:52.030 --> 43:53.340
You created Lu Wuyi

43:53.840 --> 43:54.730
to gather

43:54.880 --> 43:57.210
everyone's emotions and memories.

43:58.000 --> 43:59.770
Thus, you controlled the entire Formless Moon Sect.

44:01.920 --> 44:02.860
I've also confirmed

44:04.550 --> 44:06.460
that the fragment is inside Lu Wuyi.

44:09.480 --> 44:10.500
I don't think

44:12.320 --> 44:13.340
I can walk this road with you

44:13.340 --> 44:14.650
to the end.

44:20.280 --> 44:21.650
Because the end...

44:24.360 --> 44:25.540
The end

44:29.670 --> 44:31.060
means Lu Wuyi's death.

44:35.480 --> 44:37.090
If we want to destroy Jiu Ying completely,

44:43.150 --> 44:44.060
Lu Wuyi

44:48.510 --> 44:49.250
must die.

45:00.510 --> 45:01.170
I know

45:03.590 --> 45:04.860
I'm about to lose her.

45:08.960 --> 45:09.650
So

45:12.550 --> 45:14.250
I'll give her

45:18.070 --> 45:19.020
anything she wants.

45:20.230 --> 45:21.540
I want your heart.

45:22.230 --> 45:23.060
Will you give me that too?

45:24.400 --> 45:24.860
Yes.

45:26.360 --> 45:26.940
Do you know?

45:29.920 --> 45:31.020
In this world,

45:33.960 --> 45:35.770
no one can see the new moon.

45:44.510 --> 45:45.650
Only I can.

45:55.000 --> 45:55.730
She is

45:58.280 --> 45:59.820
my moon alone.

46:20.620 --> 46:24.740
♪See the daylight wrapped in silver light♪

46:25.820 --> 46:28.740
♪Black turns white with time passing by♪

46:29.180 --> 46:33.900
♪She holds a flower, counts the seasons slow♪

46:34.380 --> 46:36.900
♪Waiting for stone to bloom♪

46:37.260 --> 46:41.220
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

46:41.700 --> 46:45.780
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

46:46.060 --> 46:49.020
♪Why's the line we cry to say♪

46:49.900 --> 46:54.300
♪Always "don't you cry"?♪

46:54.860 --> 46:58.620
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

46:59.060 --> 47:02.940
♪Your sunrise fades into my gray♪

47:03.420 --> 47:06.820
♪You left behind your final words♪

47:07.220 --> 47:11.940
♪And every word became a scar♪

47:12.220 --> 47:16.100
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

47:16.660 --> 47:20.700
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

47:20.940 --> 47:24.020
♪Why's the line we cry to say♪

47:24.820 --> 47:29.260
♪Always "don't you cry"?♪

47:29.700 --> 47:33.580
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

47:34.140 --> 47:38.020
♪Your name's the words I long to say♪

47:38.420 --> 47:42.060
♪I call for you, my only one♪

47:42.580 --> 47:49.780
♪You're my everlasting bloom♪

48:11.260 --> 48:12.420
♪It's your light♪

48:12.620 --> 48:14.500
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

48:14.660 --> 48:17.780
♪That set the night alight♪

48:18.140 --> 48:24.660
♪And lead me through the fight♪

48:26.420 --> 48:28.300
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

48:28.740 --> 48:33.180
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

48:33.980 --> 48:35.660
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

48:35.820 --> 48:41.220
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

48:41.980 --> 48:47.380
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

48:49.700 --> 48:55.740
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

48:56.700 --> 48:58.860
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

48:59.140 --> 49:03.980
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

49:04.340 --> 49:06.660
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

49:06.860 --> 49:11.940
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

49:12.180 --> 49:14.180
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

49:14.460 --> 49:18.820
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

49:19.820 --> 49:26.780
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

49:43.340 --> 49:46.300
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

49:47.380 --> 49:50.780
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

49:51.580 --> 49:54.100
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

49:54.340 --> 49:57.420
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

49:57.820 --> 50:00.140
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

50:00.660 --> 50:05.060
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

50:05.300 --> 50:07.460
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

50:07.860 --> 50:12.820
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

50:13.060 --> 50:14.220
♪It's your light♪

50:14.420 --> 50:16.260
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

50:16.460 --> 50:19.580
♪That set the night alight♪

50:20.340 --> 50:29.780
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
